text: When your @ScottyCameron Timeless is on @FedEx truck for delivery in your town, but not running again until Monday......#patience #TourOnly https://t.co/sDjl7yocau

@TheRealCDaddy Hello Carson, my name is Rebecca. I apologize for the inconvenience you have experienced.  Would you like me to check on your delivery?  Please DM your address, tracking number, and phone number. 
Thank you.

@FedExHelp No maam. I'm just being dramatic. It's been scheduled for Monday all along, just popped up in my town this morning. Your folks need a weekend too! It's just a really really cool package, so, I gotta be patient. Thanks

Follow up. My putter showed up today and I got to tow the @FedEx guy down my driveway. Got stuck and it was only his 3rd day! Poor kid. So, we spent an hour getting him out in the rain, but, I got my @ScottyCameron #Timeless https://t.co/8ku8pKWZb3

@TheRealCDaddy Carson, 
I'm so happy to hear that you received your package and thank you for helping our driver out!  Thank you for using FedEx. We appreciate your business!  Have a wonderful day!
Thank you. 
~Rebecca

@FedExHelp You as well, ma'am. 
Also, the new kid Toby that drives a truck out of Tyler, Tx is a good one. I hope he can make a good hand for y'all.
